{"tid":2751,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"腦魔奇俠","createTime":"2016-11-26T01:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T18:17:50.000Z","uid":6489,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"345805834e34b7fec4bf12a13661eafc016fe4ed","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"如今香城大亂 成為了惡名遠昭的罪惡之城<br />\n各路罪犯都借機到來香城撈一筆大茶飯<br />\n<br />\n我 只是一名住在香城大宅 家父是拔碎集團董事長的富二代毒男 庭佳<br />\n<br />\n這一天 又看似是很平常的一天 我和父母包起了cafe de indo享用晚餐 <br />\n然而事情來得不太順利<br />\n<br />\n我不消半分鐘就把剛放上枱的黑松露營多都奉獻給我的胃後 就立馬肚痛 我當然二話不說走上廁所好好地享受一下<br />\n<br />\n甫關上廁所門 外面突然響起幾聲槍聲 頓時便意全消 整理一下理智 便知道餐廳的父母有危險 但我手無寸鐵 只能眼白白地看到一個帶著草泥馬面具的怪人捉走了我雙親<br />\n<br />\n我當時不敢相信眼前一切 只能致電給阿福求教 <br />\n<br />\n5分鐘後 阿福駛來了一架戰機岀來把我救出 <br />\n<br />\n他媽的 平日的阿褔不是手震不停的老管家 駕起戰機的樣貌都似模似樣.... 但為何會這樣 短短數十分鐘發生了這麼多事 我消化不來 <br />\n<br />\n腦超載的我眼前一黑 就昏睡了"},{"pid":"71225f356d1c87ad2397b991bcfcdced30f01361","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"一覺醒來 阿福跟我說 你父母失蹤了 生死未卜<br />\n你將會繼承拔碎集團以及家族所有資產的唯一受益人<br />\n<br />\n明天阿福就帶我去點算一下我所繼承的資產"},{"pid":"64186fb542348f9e2738a797846287e15cb7c59e","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:03:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616c089855930d37ec91f523b79144720eade30f","tid":2751,"uid":4340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61df74f4df0affa01d946d0400bdd52f732d207","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:14:37.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4aa1baac514ca7741c5073f41a20e56085c30b","tid":2751,"uid":13117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"快啲出文"},{"pid":"970add888f312c6a8921cdbc8096f00c51ef7d1e","tid":2751,"uid":1923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:27:06.000Z","msg":"好想繼續睇落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3739c966ae0b4273b3f5bbab2801940520fbe41e","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:47:40.000Z","msg":"錢 全部都係錢之外<br />\n吸引到我眼球就是一本啡黃色 舖滿灰塵的記事本<br />\n書簽是一條生銹了的鎖匙<br />\n<br />\n記事本內容就是香城未來20年的住宅規劃及合伙人名單 我爸希望為貧困的人帶來住屋的希望<br />\n<br />\n但奇怪的是中間有一頁被撕掉 然而下一頁就岀現了一隻全身綠色 伸岀一條大舌頭 表情猥瑣的奇怪圖案 <br />\n<br />\n眼前這本記事本 令我不禁懷疑是跟我父母失蹤有關 我把它放進我的褲袋 希望帶回大宅好好查明真相<br />\n<br />\n今天都太累了 所以明天才回集團召開董事會商議我的接管事宜<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"18d6a716ffa605ba4bb284f780f57a942cd1e3c9","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"再冇人理就棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42a2a5e86bbe9e7cafe2361610991506e4ed30b","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7778f61514349f3209b8a70c425e33eff3287153","tid":2751,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3d57a68c25f5578bad813a9eff7274148dd331","tid":2751,"uid":1923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efd61e9c900abd049899ba44fdbed894ab6bb6f","tid":2751,"uid":5647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d46b40c3f29b80c2ac18271d41e78480576395","tid":2751,"uid":10210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"出文啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a31e4975fb0d5956253745d103f0c65c6863b7c","tid":2751,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e90bc14264d3eb362302fd3cec4bdc5e35d3ae0","tid":2751,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T06:54:44.000Z","msg":"陳庭佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1653d947c7c694e7916a712297ac441fb6da4b87","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"回到大宅 大宅冷清得可怕 所以我立即致電給我的好友 阿源過來跟我聚一聚<br />\n<br />\n雖然他跟我一樣性格毒毒 但就搏學多才 是香城大學的圖書館管理員<br />\n<br />\n未幾 門鈴響起<br />\n<br />\n我二話不說把他帶到大宅的書房 跟他說岀了那個全身綠色東西的特徵<br />\n<br />\n只見他眼神詫異 然後不斷迴避我的問題 於是我鍥而不捨 不斷旁敲側擊 眼見他開始抵受不住我的精神折磨 終於大聲地說岀一句 不要再煩了!!<br />\n<br />\n他終於開口說岀這怪東西的來源..."},{"pid":"b4b119581f671bba3921c01049be76b8cef1af20","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be97e1fb2705815656b2d1a95e94e0446ae6085","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"原來這傢伙的名字是腦魔 當年香城被黑勢力共慘黨迫害時 香城居民被欺壓時 腦魔從天而降 一條舌頭就將共慘軍隊消滅 香城居民借機反擊 力保香城土地 可惜香城自此便不復當年繁華盛世 引來不少黃賭毒紮根....<br />\n<br />\n歷史也有記載著幾起神秘力量於戰爭中幫助弱勢一群 使他們免陷於危難之中 <br />\n<br />\n只是這力量在近百年都再沒有現身於人類眼前<br />\n<br />\n我愈聽愈入神 不慎觸碰了書房的古董花瓶 不過此花瓶卻轉了180度 書房後的牆也跟著開啟了<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"218f527e7923b3717dbd374e79f7e45d2192abf1","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T09:05:17.000Z","msg":"冇人理我"},{"pid":"b365acc72839c3093a41659902ebd1193e4c30ef","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T09:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8782f104ffffb81aba6126fbca9046f91aa9cb10","tid":2751,"uid":329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be2687a6769c6f2c71a46285448f450a82815c4","tid":2751,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fecb6c756a823b68eb5c94bfb5a0f1c3cd6b473","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb773657aaa3ffce7b05bc305cff810fb7998599","tid":2751,"uid":6489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}